<subSubSection id="33A201950D6D853D7F90F988FC391D7A" box="[199,969,1600,1625]" pageId="1" pageNumber="290" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="7B07521E0D6D853D7F90F988FC391D7A" blockId="1.[151,1437,653,1625]" box="[199,969,1600,1625]" pageId="1" pageNumber="290">
<emphasis id="49CC8E0C0D6D853D7F90F988FEBE1D7B" bold="true" box="[199,334,1600,1625]" pageId="1" pageNumber="290">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific name is derived from the species 
